data.description: Welcome to 45 Frebis Ave, an exceptional property right in the heart of Columbus! Minutes to Nationwide Children's Hospital, City Park and German Village, this home caps off an adorable street on a large corner lot! This 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home features tons of updates throughout, including new floors, fresh paint, updated lighting, stainless steel appliances and updated bathrooms! Outside highlights a covered porch to enjoy your morning coffee, a fenced in back yard, 2 parking spaces and plenty of room to build a garage!
